Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.56,0:01:23.14,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统帅千军万马的那家伙 上辈子绝对是个外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.82,0:01:28.93,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ミクロとマクロの距離感　大事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.82,0:01:28.93,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微观宏观 距离感最直观
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.05,0:01:31.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙規模での勘違い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.05,0:01:31.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这差别都用不着感官
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:34.83,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だけとね アダムとイヴ再来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:34.83,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊 亚当夏娃都能重温美好时光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:39.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ならば 猫も杓子もいっそ　このままでいいじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:39.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 咱们也这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:43.07,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほら、もっとよくみて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:43.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 再多看我一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.17,0:01:46.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほら、もっと欲張って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.17,0:01:46.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 再多想我一点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:49.71,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほら、そっう手を撮って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:49.71,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来 轻轻牵起我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.81,0:01:53.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほら、とっとと笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.81,0:01:53.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啦 快点给我笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:01.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠く遠くのBPM
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:01.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远远飞来心灵电波
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:02.98,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当に冗句の域を超えて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:02.98,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连脑残波也被超过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.09,0:02:06.57,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山を越えて　野を越えて　あいつがいる星を届く登録
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.09,0:02:06.57,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻山越岭直达他的外星王国
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.74,0:02:09.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はら、夢中だキャプテンクイーンにSOS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.74,0:02:09.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不 大家正在关注 发向女皇船长的SOS电波
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.49,0:02:11.25,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ミサイル迎撃準備よし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.49,0:02:11.25,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导弹发射准备完了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:14.82,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弾道を操るあいつはいかにも生まれる前からalien
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:14.82,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责操纵方向的那家伙 怎么看上辈子都是个外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:17.59,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今まさに宇宙はspace
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:17.59,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在整个宇宙都属于我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.19,0:02:20.80,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂一つのsweet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.19,0:02:20.80,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也就是所谓的美妙世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:24.17,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甘い甘いチューtaste
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:24.17,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜甜蜜蜜一个吻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:27.50,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂一つのsweet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:27.50,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又给世界增添了一分可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.92,0:02:29.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法は一振り
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.92,0:02:29.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻轻一挥魔杖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:31.06,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの子と二人きり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:31.06,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我便和他相依相偎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:32.87,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂糖を一振り
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:32.87,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再撒一勺砂糖满杯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:34.67,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの子はいただき
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:34.67,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就属于我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小招的露天教室已成为荒川河岸的日常景致之一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珊 明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又只问小珊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.83,0:02:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃个荒淫教师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:03:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃们两个 快点给我把从星星那里学来的玩意忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 你们要是有问题我一定会回答的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 老师 提问
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师有女朋友吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.78,0:03:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀？ 这么无聊的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家可是很认真在问你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚…亚马逊女战士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad3\4c&H4DAC32&\c&H51F7F8&\pos(322,196)}第157话「新同学亚马逊女战士」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙就是在埼玉见过的亚马逊女战士么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航空母舰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啊 我没有骗你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.91,0:03:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狗就站在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃们好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 真的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然真有亚马逊女战士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你见到我这么高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.14,0:03:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？ 还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好直接的问法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是一发抽中我们的秘密宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「卡滋卡滋大王」的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一指神功超快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？很少有短信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家是亚马逊女战士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家超喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请和我交往
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家虽然人高马大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是从打猎到烹饪能一手包办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这点一眼就能看出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走在路上五个人起码有四个会回头看我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是很佩服其中那个唯一无视你的好汉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我交往你绝不吃亏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 不可能啦 因为我有女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 就是这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:04:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿吹箭？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 不准伤害小珊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾丝手帕？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.73,0:05:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 因为外表太彪悍不经意话说重了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 以后我还能来上课吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚马逊女战士…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这姑娘其实在粗壮的外表下有一颗少女的心么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要喜欢上一个人就想待在他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦咬到猎物就要咬到只剩一堆白骨为止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么明天见 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这比喻太吓人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad3\pos(322,196)\c&H8B44EB&\4c&HF1FDFF&}第158话「爱之歌」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也来了 而且连天狗都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:06:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是小招少爷 她好像很喜欢你耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？和她交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了 我已经有小珊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何况 更重要是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会挑对象的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种体格的女性……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚马逊女战士又是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上课时间手机…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚马逊女战士 亚马逊女战士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表给我唱奇怪的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚马逊女战士 亚马逊女战士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚要…亚马逊女战士注意…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是手机…不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…裙子会不会太短了点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裙子…你是指那两片蛇皮做的防具？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:07:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.91,0:07:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为除了老师之外 这只是用来遮住所有男人视线的盾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 不要开老师的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.46,0:07:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这什么情况？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,催眠完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？真不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为体弱多病至今没上过学吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.89,0:07:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了你这副清瘦纤细的身子也不难理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么航母的体格居然说纤细
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他吃错药了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人是东施效颦 故意装的弱不禁风引起小招的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.53,0:07:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定吃了不少苦吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你不会有事的 老师会照顾你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 小招
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.08,0:07:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我认真上课
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手P子 别那么粗暴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像汗毛般轻盈的她要是被风吹走怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汗毛？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.47,0:08:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是真的体弱多病就给我多穿点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.54,0:08:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在包在你身上的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 我只有这套
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.65,0:08:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天的时候都会在身上加点什么的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不用 我不能再穿衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.91,0:08:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服太重的话 我会被压垮的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你完全就是强壮到冬天都可以只穿短裤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad3\4c&H4DAC32&\c&H51F7F8&\pos(322,196)}第159话「波涛汹涌的爱」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不正常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小招看亚马逊女战士的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}小珊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一直都那样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙看我和其他居民的时候基本都是这眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者这种
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至这种
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:09:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看亚马逊女战士的眼神竟然就像在看小珊一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他最近老和亚马逊女战士粘在一起不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啊 他一直和我一起吃午饭的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小招
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正打算给你送饭去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 小珊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天学生给我做了便当
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这咋全是埼玉畅销的古早味零嘴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚我们还为了这个笑成一团呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似这个超受欢迎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 我居然用她的口气说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 不快点吃掉的话会化的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 那么等会见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啊 我马上就会吃的 你干嘛急
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师这超好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊 这是没办法的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小珊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么回河里去吧 小招的午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珊 那个已经烤过了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是受不了了就发泄出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？到河口约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 好久没去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧去吧 今天如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点左右来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心吧 我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小珊约会啊 千万不能迟到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚马逊女战士偷取古物现在正在亚马逊警署接受辅导？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 在马丘比丘…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}マチュビチュ 又译作麻丘比丘，是秘鲁一个著名的前哥伦布时期时印加帝国的遗迹，也是世界新七大奇迹之一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:10:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…她父母呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲在她小时候就过世了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲出门打猎一直没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 也就是说现在她一个人孤零零在警署？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没关系 只是关她一夜让她反省下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是打个电话通知下老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 她一定是太寂寞才会去偷东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚马逊女战士你为什么要做这种傻事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为偷东西就能引起某人注意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚马逊女战士别再做这种傻事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一辈子看着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我要你好好承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小招 你怎么了 迟到…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有重要的话要和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在亚马逊市民政局
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办理了入籍手续
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈情说爱貌似比坐云霄飞车要刺激多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad3\pos(322,196)\c&H853EE3&\4c&HFFFFFF&}第160话「爱情表现」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们为了入籍所以来迟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}(牛奶)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}(椅子)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}(牛奶+椅子=乳席)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}日文中"入"和"乳"都发为にゅう而"籍"和"席"都发成せき
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有教养啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个孩子可是可怜的孤女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须由我来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我没办法继续和你交往下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珊 我们分手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打耳光？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也只能用这种方式赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 小珊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:13:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你打几个耳光 我都…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身上？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小珊的心情 我已经完全体会到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.11,0:13:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要用拳头来表达我的心情的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一拳压根不算什么 我至少还会朝你肚子上揍一百拳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到很吵 于是凑过来一瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是修罗场么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且小招要和小珊分手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不敢相信 你居然对老师动粗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你也听到了吧 我们已经办理了入籍手续
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这眼神还真是不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:14:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我看看你有多么爱老师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？ 小珊你怎么可以和那种野战的种族决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 小珊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有这么爱老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有这么爱小招
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我爱老师这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我爱小招已经多到河里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我对小珊的爱有一百个东京巨蛋那么大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.28,0:14:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在龟有病的后遗症作祟下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星也开始加入女孩们的决斗行列
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad3\4c&H4DAC32&\c&H51F7F8&\pos(322,196)}第161话 「决不放弃」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能输给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的是你的两倍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珊也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种傻X到底哪一点好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:15:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然丢下小珊 投入那大象女的怀抱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小珊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？ 乃要吃回头草么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱 亚马逊女战士好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清瘦白皙的亚马逊女战士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚马逊女战士 你是美丽的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是乃们几个搞的鬼 让他变成这副德行的么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.09,0:15:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 居然被你识破了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你应该会为我们保密吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为对你来说 这是天上掉下来的馅饼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的「亚马逊女战士恋情支援计划」若是成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫小珊的女孩就是你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚马逊女战士 亚马逊女战士 清瘦可爱的亚马逊女战士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚马逊女战士…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能与你相守 我真是幸福死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:16:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的前任女友小珊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女生很受欢迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 即使没有我 她也不会寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我不守护在她身边 也没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了啊 这是什么声音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊 这么大个圈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.07,0:16:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的爱可不只有大小而已哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以换算成高度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么高
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚马逊女战士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要硬撑啊 不要一个劲的跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.37,0:16:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？ 她的身体状况没准是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 你精力太充沛了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然身体不好 但是照顾老师还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小招也因为有气喘 身体不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.36,0:16:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小招由我来照顾就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与此同时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西边 河童大力士 河童大力士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.74,0:17:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招兵买马挑战 招兵买马挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好叻 绝不会输给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我秒杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小招在梦中 正在准备春季相扑比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.96,0:17:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad3\4c&H4DAC32&\c&H51F7F8&\pos(322,196)}第162话「响起吧！爱之歌」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长 不要找我当练习的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这家伙的梦变得很奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珊爱的面积
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:18:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珊爱的高度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.15,0:18:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是小珊爱的体积
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你是职业歌手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此就来帮我唱催眠之歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 撮合亚马逊女战士和小招对你有好处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就来帮…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.69,0:18:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.13,0:18:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「爱」可不是什么天上掉下来的馅饼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.84,0:18:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珊那边可真是热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边只有两个人 不免有些冷清
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就多增加几个我 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 亚马逊女战士100个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比那边热闹…多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？ 要来1000个么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:18:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:18:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.94,0:19:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是1000个亚马逊女战士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是这世上唯一的小珊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像做了很久的噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然自行解开了催眠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新娘礼服…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么说果然这一切都是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚…亚马逊女战士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 虽然我说过一辈子要和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我果然还是对小珊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认输
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚马逊女战士…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.69,0:19:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有「今天」而已哦 明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚马逊女战士~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:20:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为毛刚刚那一瞬间我会觉得她好可爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行 不行 我已经有小珊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小招
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起 我貌似闯了不得了的祸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也来「乳席」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！ 难道说小珊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.96,0:20:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来「入席」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}"籍"和"席"发音都为せき "入"和"乳"都为にゅう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头一定要转向这边么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是「乳席」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.19,0:20:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在荒川河上游
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:20:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以锻炼肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.58,0:21:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我练着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是越挫越勇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.39,0:21:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对小招无法死心的亚马逊女战士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.19,0:21:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了增强体力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说买了比利牌肌肉健美机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:31.14,edc,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,旅途结束时不由想起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:31.14,edj,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,旅の終りに　思うもの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.70,0:21:37.62,edc,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,曾经那些一味追寻的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.70,0:21:37.62,edj,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,求めるだけの日々は過ぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.67,0:21:43.15,edc,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,欢呼雀跃 欣然期盼冬天来临
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.67,0:21:43.15,edj,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,冬を待たずにはしゃいでる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:49.51,edc,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,那裹着红外套的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:49.51,edj,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,赤いコート包まれる君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:52.64,edc,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 那些迷惘的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:52.64,edj,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,さよなら迷宮days
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.65,0:21:55.27,edc,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,如今回首往事 thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.65,0:21:55.27,edj,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,気付けばthank youです
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.35,0:21:58.07,edc,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,So oh oh
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.35,0:21:58.07,edj,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,そう　oh oh
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.12,0:22:00.82,edc,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye days
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.12,0:22:00.82,edj,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye days
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:16.14,edc,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,旅程开始时不由想到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:16.14,edj,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,旅の始まりに　思うもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.57,0:22:22.44,edc,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,深深呼吸 大步前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.57,0:22:22.44,edj,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,立ち止まらすに深呼吸する
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.63,0:22:28.09,edc,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,和你去畅游未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.63,0:22:28.09,edj,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,二人明日を泳いでる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:34.55,edc,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,并肩相伴 畅游人生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:34.55,edj,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,魚みたいに並び揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.68,0:22:37.55,edc,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦吗？ No thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.68,0:22:37.55,edj,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,辛い？ No thank you　です
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.65,0:22:40.28,edc,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,悲伤吗？No thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.65,0:22:40.28,edj,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,悲しい　no thank you　です
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.36,0:22:42.77,edc,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,So oh oh
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.36,0:22:42.77,edj,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,そう　oh oh
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.82,0:22:44.57,edc,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye days
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.82,0:22:44.57,edj,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye days
